# Cloudflare Pages/Netlify-compatible redirects for HonestInvoice
# 1) Force HTTPS and canonical domain (www -> apex)
http://www.honestinvoice.com/* https://honestinvoice.com/:splat 301!
http://honestinvoice.com/*     https://honestinvoice.com/:splat 301!
https://www.honestinvoice.com/* https://honestinvoice.com/:splat 301!

# 2) Legacy URL redirects to current routes
/signin      /auth 301
/sign-in     /auth 301
/login       /auth 301
/register    /auth 301
/signup      /auth 301

# 3) Trailing slash normalization (explicit safe routes)
/auth/       /auth 301
/dashboard/  /dashboard 301

# 4) SPA routing fallback (must be last)
/*           /index.html 200

